影片于2014年3月24日开拍，5月12日杀青<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.studiosystemnews.com/on-the-set-for-32414/ |title=‘On The Set’ For 3/24/14: Nicole Kidman Starts ‘Strangerland’, ‘Frankenstein’ Wraps For 20th Century Fox |publisher=Studiosystemnews.com |date= |accessdate=2014-03-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140329093742/http://www.studiosystemnews.com/on-the-set-for-32414/ |archivedate=2014-03-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Rosser |first=Michael |url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/absolutely-anything-wraps-shoot/5071550.article |title=Terry Jones’ Absolutely Anything starring Simon Pegg wraps shoot |publisher=Screendaily.com |date=2014-05-12 |accessdate=2014-07-08}}</ref>。导演琼斯表示：“影片在伦敦拍了六个星期。我们接管了离我不远的香雪巷（{{lang|en|Hornsey Lane}}）一家荒废的学校。我们在那儿搭了个摄影棚，把它用作基地。之后，我们拍了[[伯爵宫|伯爵宫]]的内景<ref>{{cite web|last=Doctor |first=Film |url=http://filmdoctor.co.uk/2015/04/15/in-conversation-terry-jones-director-absolutely-anything-monty-python-and-the-holy-grail-life-of-brian-wind-in-the-willows/ |title=Terry Jones In Conversation |publisher=Filmdoctor.co.uk |date=2015-05-01 |accessdate=2014-07-08}}</ref>。”3月28日，[[狮门影业|狮门英国]]宣布将在英国发行影片<ref name="screendaily1"/>。

== 音乐 ==
澳大利亚歌手[[凯莉·米洛|凯莉·米洛]]为原声带录制并发行宣传单曲《Absolutely Anything and Anything At All》<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/absolutely-anything-anything/id1024984178?app=itunes&ign-mpt=uo%3D4 |title=iTunes - Music - Absolutely Anything and Anything At All (From "Absolutely Anything") - Single by Kylie Minogue |publisher=iTunes |accessdate=2015-08-08}}</ref>。音乐录影带于米洛的官方YouTube频道发布<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FrSTw4D1348 |title=Kylie - Absolutely Anything and Anything At All |publisher=Kylie Minogue Official Channel |date=2015-08-07 |accessdate=2016-08-25}}</ref>。

== 发行 ==
首批剧照于2014年10月30日公布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.mtime.com/2014/10/30/1533351.html |title=西蒙佩吉新片曝首批剧照 搭档贝金赛尔演绎搞笑科幻 |publisher=[[时光网|Mtime时光网]] |date=2014-10-30 |accessdate=2016-08-25 |language=zh-cn}}</ref>，而正式版预告片则于2015年5月4日亮相<ref>{{cite web|last=Chavez |first=Paul |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3068158/Trailer-Robin-Williams-British-comedy-Absolutely-debuts-voices-character-dog.html |title=Something to bark about: Trailer for Robin Williams' British comedy Absolutely Anything debuts as he voices the character of a dog |publisher=Mail Online |date=2015-05-05 |accessdate=2016-08-25}}</ref>。

影片于2015年8月14日由[[狮门影业|狮门英国]]在英国发行<ref>{{cite web |last=Foutch |first=Haleigh |url=http://collider.com/absolutely-anything-trailer-gives-simon-pegg-the-power/ |title=Absolutely Anything Trailer Gives Simon Pegg the Power |publisher=Collider |date=2015-05-03 |accessdate=2015-05-04 |archive-date=2015-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150506224601/http://collider.com/absolutely-anything-trailer-gives-simon-pegg-the-power/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并于5月28日和10月2日分别在香港和台湾上映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://hk.movies.nextmedia.com/movie/absolutely-anything/ |title=Absolutely Anything - 一台戲– 蘋果日報 |publisher=[[苹果日报_(香港)|苹果日报]] |accessdate=2016-08-25 |language=zh-hk}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://app2.atmovies.com.tw/film/fauk41727770/ |title=超能玩很大--Absolutely Anything @movies【開眼電影網】 |publisher=[[开眼电影网|开眼电影网]] |accessdate=2016-08-25 |language=zh-tw}}</ref>。内地定档2016年9月9日上映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.mtime.com/2016/08/15/1558646.html |title=西蒙佩吉《魔法老师》定档9月9日 联袂贝金赛尔演绎爆笑喜剧 曝光先导海报&预告 |publisher=[[时光网|Mtime时光网]] |date=2016-08-15 |accessdate=2016-08-25 |language=zh-cn}}</ref>。

== 评价 ==
在[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上，影片获得了基于33条评论打出的15%的新鲜度，平均分3.3分（满分10分）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/absolutely_anything/ |title=Absolutely Anything (2015) |work=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Flixster |accessdate=2015-12-01}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]从主流评论家的评论中，按照100分满分的原则，根据6条评论给影片打出34的[[加权平均数|加权平均分]]，表示“普遍差评”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/absolutely-anything |title=Absolutely Anything Reviews |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=CBS Interactive |accessdate=2015-08-24}}</ref>。《[[卫报|卫报]]》作家彼得·布拉德肖（{{lang|en|Peter Bradshaw}}）给予影片1星（满分5星，下同）的评价，称“廉价、惨淡的科幻喜剧。虽然有炙手可热的演员、有特里·琼斯的导演、有派森家族客串令人毛骨悚然的外星生物，但是这部预算低的英国电影只是一部郁闷的、次道格拉斯·亚当斯科幻喜剧，看上去像是剧本令人沮丧，制作价值廉价且平淡的平庸儿童电视节目。大量人才聚集在此，可悲的是，这是条死胡同<ref>{{cite web|title=Absolutely Anything review - cheap and cheerless sci-fi comedy|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/aug/13/absolutely-anything-review-cheap-and-cheerless-sci-fi-comedy|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2016-05-28}}</ref>。”《{{le|The List|The List (magazine)}}》的詹姆斯·莫特拉姆（{{lang|en|James Mottram}}）也给予影片1星，并表示：“西蒙·佩吉和凯特·贝金赛尔领衔了一部可怕的特里·琼斯科幻喜剧片。如果这算是派森最后一部荧屏合作作品，是非常沮丧的<ref>{{cite web|title=Simon Pegg and Kate Beckinsale head up an awful sci-fi comedy from Terry Jones|url=https://film.list.co.uk/article/73448-absolutely-anything/|work=The List|accessdate=2016-05-28}}</ref>。”

